                        <i>
                          The great caliphs : the golden age of the 'Abbasid Empire
                        </i>
                        . New Haven: 
                        <a href="/wiki/Yale_University_Press" title="Yale University Press">
                          Yale University Press
                        </a>
                        . p. 187. 
                        <a href="/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number">
                          ISBN
                        </a>
                         
